The paper discusses the application of information theory to psychological problems and proposes a mathematical approach inspired by Ausubel's meaningful learning theory. It also discusses the computational theory of mind and the two assumed systems of cognitive functioning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.CC (Computational Complexity), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
